404
00:31:24,132 --> 00:31:26,216
that brought my husband to his death,

405
00:31:26,301 --> 00:31:29,928
and if l can qualify
as an airplane worker at Vega

406
00:31:30,013 --> 00:31:32,431
and with my hands
help to keep 'em flying,

407
00:31:32,515 --> 00:31:35,017
l will feel
that l am carrying on for him.

408
